OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike could cost
OL,4,Ccouncil #26m if deal isn't reached
OL,6,FBirmingham's long-running bin dispute
OL,7,Fcould end up costing the city council
OL,8,Faround #26 million, according to
OL,9,Ffinancial investigators.
OL,11,FThey estimate that if the strike lasts
OL,12,Funtil the end of its current mandate
OL,13,Fin March, the already effectively
OL,14,Fbankrupt authority will have spent
OL,15,Fmore than Unite the Union is asking
OL,16,Ffor in one-off payments to affected
OL,17,Fworkers.
