OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike could cost
OL,4,Ccouncil #26m if deal isn't reached
OL,6,FHowever, the council's leader says he
OL,7,Fdoes not recognise the figure and
OL,8,Finsists any pay-offs to settle the
OL,9,Fdispute could expose the council to
OL,10,Ffurther equal pay claims.
OL,12,FVivek Kotecha, from Trinava
OL,13,FConsulting, has used the council's own
OL,14,Fpublic documents to estimate the
OL,15,Ffinancial impact of the ongoing
OL,16,Findustrial action.
OL,18,FHe said that if the strike were to
OL,19,Fstop in November, the council could
OL,20,Fsave up to around #11 million or #11.5
OL,21,Fmillion.
