OL,6,F"I've looked at what Unite has put
OL,7,Fforward and it's about #14,000 to
OL,8,F#20,000 compensation per worker," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"That's obviously subject to
OL,12,Fnegotiation, but they would still,
OL,13,Feven after paying compensation, be
OL,14,Fsaving money overall if they ended the
OL,15,Fstrike sooner rather than later.
OL,17,F"So I think for the council, it seems
OL,18,Fwin-win for them to end this strike
OL,19,Fand agree on something with Unite."
