OL,3,CBirmingham bin strike could cost
OL,4,Ccouncil #26m if deal isn't reached
OL,6,FAccording to Birmingham City Council's
OL,7,Flatest financial report, the strike
OL,8,Fhas already cost the authority around
OL,9,F#14 million.
OL,11,FAround #9.6 million of that has been
OL,12,Fspent on one-off costs such as street
OL,13,Fcleaning, extended waste centre hours,
OL,14,Fsecurity and clean-up operations,
OL,15,Fwhile a further #4.4 million has been
OL,16,Flost in income from the city's green
OL,17,Fwaste service, which has been
OL,18,Fsuspended for the year and refunded to
OL,19,Fresidents.
