OL,6,F"It's not a figure I recognise," he
OL,7,Fsaid. "We will be bringing forward
OL,8,Freports to cabinet that set out some
OL,9,Fof the costs of the contingencies that
OL,10,Fwe've had to put in place, but it's
OL,11,Freally important that we have those
OL,12,Fcontingencies in place so we've been
OL,13,Fable to continue to empty bins across
OL,14,Fthe city."
OL,16,FHe added: "The fundamental point I
OL,17,Fcome back to is, I am not going to put
OL,18,Fthis council into a position where we
OL,19,Fcreate a further equal pay injustice,
OL,20,Fand that again costs the taxpayers of
OL,21,Fthe city even more money.
